reviewText: Ok this is one of my favorite Kay Francis movies, mainly because I got an idea for my new front door from the doors of Kay's dress design studio.  Also, she looks great in her highly fashionable (for 1932) gowns.  Just a good pre Hayes code 30's movie.
I love Kay Francis. So beautiful, elegant, chic and I have loved every one of the movies she ever made.  I want them all
